    <string name="manual_content">üì± B1gBr0ther - Complete User Manual\n\n
üéØ OVERVIEW\n
B1gBr0ther is a comprehensive time tracking and task management app that uses voice commands, gesture recognition, and smart audio detection to help you track your work efficiently.\n\n

‚è∞ TIME TRACKING\n
‚Ä¢ Create and manage tasks with start/end times\n
‚Ä¢ Track time spent on different activities\n
‚Ä¢ Take breaks and monitor break time\n
‚Ä¢ View your progress with visual timers\n
‚Ä¢ Tasks auto-save to database\n\n

üó£Ô∏è VOICE COMMANDS\n
Enable in Settings ‚Üí Audio Settings ‚Üí Voice Commands\n\n
Task Control:\n
‚Ä¢ \"Start tracking [task name]\" - Begin timing a task\n
‚Ä¢ \"Stop tracking\" / \"I\'m done\" - End current task\n
‚Ä¢ \"Take a break\" / \"Start break\" - Begin break time\n
‚Ä¢ \"Stop break\" / \"Back to work\" - End break\n
‚Ä¢ \"Delete task [name]\" - Remove a task\n\n
Navigation:\n
‚Ä¢ \"Show export\" / \"Export data\" - Open export page\n
‚Ä¢ \"Show manual\" / \"Show help\" - Open this manual\n
‚Ä¢ \"Show timesheet\" / \"View my hours\" - View calendar\n
‚Ä¢ \"Show statistics\" / \"Show stats\" - View analytics\n\n
Export Commands:\n
‚Ä¢ \"Export CSV\" / \"Export JSON\" / \"Export HTML\"\n
‚Ä¢ \"Export Markdown\" / \"Export XML\" / \"Export text\"\n\n

üéµ SMART AUDIO DETECTION\n
Enable in Settings ‚Üí Audio Settings ‚Üí Sound Detection\n\n
‚Ä¢ Blow Detection: Detects when you blow (offers smoke break)\n
‚Ä¢ Sneeze Detection: Says \"Bless you!\" when you sneeze\n
‚Ä¢ Bathroom Break Detection: Recognizes urination sounds\n
‚Ä¢ Adjustable sensitivity settings\n\n

üëã GESTURE RECOGNITION\n
Enable in Settings ‚Üí Motion &amp; Gesture Detection\n\n
‚Ä¢ Shake Detection: Shake device to trigger actions\n
‚Ä¢ Directional Gestures: Left, right, up, down movements\n
‚Ä¢ Accelerometer-based: Uses device motion sensors\n
‚Ä¢ Create tasks through gesture dialogs\n\n

üìä DASHBOARD\n
Your main control center:\n
‚Ä¢ Real-time timer display\n
‚Ä¢ Current task status\n
‚Ä¢ Weekly time visualization grid\n
‚Ä¢ Quick access to all features\n
‚Ä¢ Voice recognition status indicator\n\n

üìÖ TIMESHEET\n
Monthly calendar view:\n
‚Ä¢ Heat-map shows work intensity per day\n
‚Ä¢ Click any day to see detailed task breakdown\n
‚Ä¢ Navigate between months and years\n
‚Ä¢ Color-coded based on hours worked\n\n

üìà STATISTICS\n
Comprehensive analytics:\n
‚Ä¢ Task completion pie charts\n
‚Ä¢ Timing analysis (early/on-time/late)\n
‚Ä¢ Creation method breakdown (voice vs gesture)\n
‚Ä¢ Quick stats: total tasks, completion rate\n\n

üì§ EXPORT FEATURES\n
Export your data in multiple formats:\n
‚Ä¢ CSV - Spreadsheet compatible\n
‚Ä¢ JSON - Developer friendly\n
‚Ä¢ HTML - Web viewable\n
‚Ä¢ Markdown - Documentation format\n
‚Ä¢ XML - Structured data\n
‚Ä¢ Plain Text - Simple format\n\n
Filtering Options:\n
‚Ä¢ Date range selection\n
‚Ä¢ Filter by completion status\n
‚Ä¢ Include/exclude breaks\n
‚Ä¢ Preplanned tasks filter\n\n

‚öôÔ∏è SETTINGS\n
Customize your experience:\n\n
Themes:\n
‚Ä¢ Light Mode (Purple theme)\n
‚Ä¢ Dark Mode (Gray theme)\n\n
Languages:\n
‚Ä¢ English, Dutch, French supported\n
‚Ä¢ Automatic UI translation\n\n
Audio Settings:\n
‚Ä¢ Off - No audio features\n
‚Ä¢ Voice Commands - Speech recognition\n
‚Ä¢ Sound Detection - Audio pattern recognition\n
‚Ä¢ Microphone permission required\n\n
Notifications:\n
‚Ä¢ Task reminders and alerts\n
‚Ä¢ Completion notifications\n
‚Ä¢ Permission-based settings\n\n

üéÆ EASTER EGG\n
Hidden Doodle Jump game:\n
‚Ä¢ Tilt device to control character\n
‚Ä¢ Jump on platforms to score points\n
‚Ä¢ High score tracking\n
‚Ä¢ Pause and resume functionality\n
‚Ä¢ Access through secret gesture combination\n\n

üîß DATABASE FEATURES\n
‚Ä¢ Local Room database storage\n
‚Ä¢ Task history preservation\n
‚Ä¢ Backup and restore capabilities\n
‚Ä¢ Performance optimized queries\n\n

üì± NAVIGATION\n
Bottom menu bar provides quick access:\n
‚Ä¢ Export (index 0)\n
‚Ä¢ Manual (index 1) \n
‚Ä¢ Dashboard (index 2)\n
‚Ä¢ Timesheet (index 3)\n
‚Ä¢ Statistics (index 4)\n\n

üí° TIPS\n
‚Ä¢ Speak naturally - the app understands variations\n
‚Ä¢ Use gestures when voice isn\'t practical\n
‚Ä¢ Enable notifications for better task tracking\n
‚Ä¢ Export data regularly for backup\n
‚Ä¢ Check statistics to improve productivity\n
‚Ä¢ Adjust audio sensitivity in noisy environments\n\n

üîí PERMISSIONS\n
Required permissions:\n
‚Ä¢ Microphone - Voice commands and sound detection\n
‚Ä¢ Notifications - Task alerts and reminders\n
‚Ä¢ Storage - Export file saving\n\n

‚ùì TROUBLESHOOTING\n
‚Ä¢ Voice not working? Check microphone permission\n
‚Ä¢ Gestures not detected? Enable accelerometer\n
‚Ä¢ Export failing? Check storage permission\n
‚Ä¢ App crashes? Try reset settings to defaults\n\n
For best experience, enable all features and grant required permissions!</string>
    
